author: arkurth
msg: Added Windows.pm::get_public_ip_address subroutine. It overloads the one in OS.pm. It contains added logic to try to detect invalid public IP addresses (169.254.*.*, 0.0.0.0). If this is detected, ipconfig /renew is run and the network configuration is retrieved again.
